nodes.text: Anjali was a female smuggler from the Inner Rim planet Onderon. At some point between 21 ABY and 35 ABY, Anjali visited Black Spire Outpost on the Outer Rim planet Batuu and was given directions by farmer Julen Rakab. His friends, musicians Fawn and Neelo, later believed that he had been attracted to her. As they teased Rakab for his bad romantic decisions, he outwardly denied their claims and cut off further conversation about Anjali.
Anjali was mentioned in A Crash of Fate, a 2019 young-adult novel written by Zoraida Córdova.
